{"tid":155616,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Oral三年5**分析歷屆題目範疇","createTime":"2017-03-14T07:33:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-17T14:30:36.000Z","uid":80833,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f5979a22af90121a056601c217ffcdac6bdb9c25","tid":155616,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:33:34.000Z","msg":"各位巴打唔好意思，原本打算早d分析歷屆oral出題理念。但係自己本身學業繁忙，又要幫學生練oral，所以宜家先出。<br />\n希望可以盡可能幫一陣考既學生溫習，遲d考既學生都可以討論下。<br />\n我考左四年dse，第一年oral 4，之後三年oral都係5**。<br />\n<br />\n之所以係咁，因爲參考完考評報告，同埋自我經驗，分析左大致出題方向。<br />\n<br />\n考評報告指出題目出自四大範疇<br />\n1.校園生活<br />\n2.社會時事<br />\n3.文化反思<br />\n4.人生價值<br />\n<br />\n而呢四樣野環環相扣，都係指向中國文化或者西方哲學。當中側重於中國文化。<br />\n<br />\n而我就參考此四範疇，分成大概十種出題範疇，可供大家參考一下，或者有所裨益。<br />\n<br />\n利申：<br />\n考左四年dse，今年都有報名，聽日就係去考oral<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目的係為左更了解考試制度，同埋補習個陣更加得心應手。"},{"pid":"1c3a0c110f63b23db8743e449ab3c53d4275c5d0","tid":155616,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:36:52.000Z","msg":"1. 五倫相處之道<br />\n● 坦誠相向：「信者人言也。」真誠地說出自己的想法，并不會掩蓋自我意見。<br />\n● 相規以善：「如切如磋，如琢如磨。」朋友要指出對方不足，互為改善。梁國雄與曾玉成在《跟著矛盾去旅行》一程中互相指出對方理念不足之處。<br />\n● 寬容待人：「君子和而不同」即便理念不同都會為之和平相處。如宋朝朱熹和陸九淵對儒家看法不同，前者秉持格物致知，後者秉持心性之學，雙方也能互相交流。朱熹說：「兼取兩家之長，不輕相詆毀。」<br />\n● 幽默風趣：間接說理，幽默說教<br />\n● 以文會友：互相交流文化，增進學識。李白和杜甫常常交流詩詞，杜甫更寫：「何時一樽酒，重與細論文」以說明雙方常常切磋學問。<br />\n● 以友輔仁：互相改善品德<br />\n● 題目舉例<br />\n● 「與人相處之道，以下哪一種最為可貴」坦率 寬厚 幽默<br />\n● 「要維繫友誼，以下哪種做法最合適? 」經常會面 坦誠相向 投其所好<br />\n● 「面面俱圓這種待人態度，有人認為能促使和諧的人際關係，亦有人認為會令人變得虛偽。試談談你的看法。」<br />\n● 「與其指正朋友錯處，不如包容其缺失，你同意嗎」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五倫<br />\n1.古代為父子 兄弟 君臣 夫妻 朋友<br />\n2.現今為家人 朋友 上司下屬 夫妻 <br />\n<br />\n而其中友道精神係貫穿左當中五倫之中<br />\n一旦講與人相處，就可以從以上理念去思考及拓展。"},{"pid":"0d1184a2c9340393e8c611599a5cc08bd7a335c5","tid":155616,"uid":24331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:40:45.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講下你發言次數大約係幾多到？"},{"pid":"6e11bd945ad47d9f9deab69336e585f3599b7497","tid":155616,"uid":72491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:50:13.000Z","msg":"留名學野"},{"pid":"f628d92f88bc5a3687e9ec6073788f70c51094b6","tid":155616,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:51:20.000Z","msg":"3. 教育觀念<br />\n● 啟發式教育：「教育是一顆靈魂喚醒另外一顆靈魂」蘇格拉底啟發式教育<br />\n● 放手式教育：「不必追」龍應台，對安德烈就是如此，與其一起寫書。<br />\n● 品德教育：岳飛母親在其背上寫精忠報國<br />\n● 基礎教育：打下知識基礎，冰心母親要求其堅持每日讀書兩三小時<br />\n*需要剛柔並濟，時而嚴厲，時而鬆弛。<br />\n <br />\n-「以下何者最能象徵父母之角色 木 土 水」<br />\n-「父母愛子女的心無微不至，會造成溺愛」你有什麼看法？"},{"pid":"617deb036d1420fb791e3c637696bd14a21c8028","tid":155616,"uid":64977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:51:56.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"b03ac5441b43eb60d5d9fd5b3f3829299ad57ead","tid":155616,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:53:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以講下你發言次數大約係幾多到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議四次<br />\n但係我試過講三次都可以5**"},{"pid":"2eb657577520066a412c5fd571f87dfb991a945d","tid":155616,"uid":24331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:55:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以講下你發言次數大約係幾多到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議四次<br />\n但係我試過講三次都可以5**</blockquote><br />\n加埋首輪？"},{"pid":"50ecff52669ef1a5078b205a14a9b054c3e0dcef","tid":155616,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:57:07.000Z","msg":"4. 社會環境<br />\n● 香港存在問題：深層次矛盾「文化矛盾（本地 VS 內地）、貧富懸殊、政治矛盾（政制、泛民 VS 建制、素人政治）、結構矛盾」<br />\n● 表層問題：勞動力不足、青年失業率、產業單一化<br />\n<br />\n適用概念<br />\n-誠信-》管制效能高<br />\n-惻隱之心-》仁政<br />\n-多數人暴政<br />\n-民粹主義<br />\n-整體利益不應凌駕個人利益<br />\n<br />\n● 為了讓香港人反思既有的生活方式，下列哪一項活動最值得提倡？試討論並達成共識。<br />\n● 面對香港現今社會環境，你認為同舟共濟還是創新求變的精神更值得提倡？談談你的看法。<br />\n● 以下都是現代社會公民應有的素養，何者最為重要？試談談你的看法。 包容異見 秉持公德 尊重隱私<br />\n● 以下均是使社會安定的方法，試就其重要性排列優次。 百姓不愁溫飽 政府取信於民 社會治安良好<br />\n● 以下各項均是理想社會不可或缺的，試就其重要性排列優次 安全 自由 平等<br />\n● 有人說，大學畢業生去做快餐店基層員工，是大材小用，你同意嗎.?"},{"pid":"64cbe5652899b3803eea06364a91e68da92c504a","tid":155616,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T07:57:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以講下你發言次數大約係幾多到？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n建議四次<br />\n但係我試過講三次都可以5**</blockquote><br />\n加埋首輪？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係<br />\n首輪係包括其中"},{"pid":"89491b57e42af247c9b8ed0367c6924e05c12512","tid":155616,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:02:06.000Z","msg":"5.個人成長<br />\n● 自強不息（品德）：史鐵生一生病疾，堅持寫作<br />\n● 堅持不懈（行為）：林書豪在美國職籃一路不平坦，亦能堅持到底<br />\n● 追求夢想（決心）：陳德恩放下紋身師傅工作，毅然追夢<br />\n● 獨立自主（能力）：蘇世豪環島夢，獨自完成<br />\n● 人情世故（智慧）：李嘉誠自小為維修學徒，銷售員，侍應<br />\n● 負面例子：玻璃孩子，二十二連跳<br />\n<br />\n-以下各項都是香港青少年常見的問題，哪項最值得關注？ 抗逆力低/自我中心/過份依賴.<br />\n-以下那樣對青少年成長最為重要。機會 挫折 夢想<br />\n<br />\n*必出範疇，希望考生反思自我問題，探索人生價值，日後前途出路，培養社會責任感，擔當社會大樑。"},{"pid":"dff6d2ea5781054c5ad13693fd2d272f6938457c","tid":155616,"uid":42048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:17:04.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"b7f7205186b249ec3714c82de62492359fa4e9aa","tid":155616,"uid":63133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T08:17:10.000Z","msg":"共識題需要轉胎嗎？"},{"pid":"eb40fe79c4c53a309615877de8e425e173dc484c","tid":155616,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T09:10:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共識題需要轉胎嗎？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有共識傾向就足夠<br />\n無話一定要轉軚"},{"pid":"a4624d2eddbda40f4eccf1481ace6f41c3ae6a50","tid":155616,"uid":7847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T15:52:43.000Z","msg":"more<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f849466bb2194adb208ba1c77d8a15fc905e27","tid":155616,"uid":5053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T16:51:19.000Z","msg":"共識題幾時轉軚會好d？同埋點轉先靚仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申聽日考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9859b76740efa4da0566fb9aa19d3f57a3fc8a37","tid":155616,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T18:29:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共識題幾時轉軚會好d？同埋點轉先靚仔？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申聽日考<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一次要講自己立場好處一<br />\n第二次要講自己立場好處二<br />\n第三次嘗試去轉立場，先講出自己壞處，再講他人立場好處。<br />\n第四次再加入對方立場討論。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c115c53aae9c52a8df2105fefc05606704b76413","tid":155616,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T07:16:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9aea1254ef3d47580008b87828ae2c02f505d160","tid":155616,"uid":391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T16:54:40.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 22號考"},{"pid":"7a5b7cb072d63a0bf846908d4bb36808b690dca6","tid":155616,"uid":80833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T04:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdd3a1fd59a3f0031a07ba72eeb912b9612ce317","tid":155616,"uid":72026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:44:22.000Z","msg":"巴打 <br />\n我真係好驚<br />\n可唔可以講下星期一會出咩題型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b48607fb95a915bc6d4020c16ef643e262c78917","tid":155616,"uid":72046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T14:27:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 <br />\n我真係好驚<br />\n可唔可以講下星期一會出咩題型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n先知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":